nagios-plugins-bird (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * added plugins-metadata for check_bird (in a unusal destination in 
    Ubuntu, but nagios configuration directory in pacemaker seems to
    be transfered from the SuSE system)

  * renamed check_bird_proto to check_bird which is more equal to the
    other check_* tests

  * changed API from -p|--protocol to -i|--instance which is also more
    equal to other check_* tests and IMHO easier to understand.

